column3: Days 1–4 Weather SummaryLight rain (total 7mm), mostly falling on Mon night. Freeze-thaw conditions (max 4°C on Sun afternoon, min -2°C on Tue night). Wind will be generally light.
column4: Days 5–7 Weather SummaryHeavy rain (total 47mm), heaviest during Fri morning. Very mild (max 12°C on Fri morning, min 1°C on Wed afternoon). Winds increasing (calm on Thu morning, fresh winds from the S by Fri morning).
column5: Days 8–10 Weather SummaryHeavy rain (total 24mm), heaviest during Sat night. Very mild (max 11°C on Sun morning, min 4°C on Mon night). Winds decreasing (fresh winds from the SW on Sun morning, calm by Mon afternoon).
column6: Days 11–13 Weather SummaryModerate rain (total 18mm), heaviest on Fri afternoon. Mild temperatures (max 8°C on Thu morning, min 2°C on Tue night). Winds increasing (calm on Tue afternoon, fresh winds from the SSW by Fri afternoon).
